message.body: My computer died again! Arg. I guess I'm buying a Mac after all!
Do sorry. We just ole up from a long nap
Winter is a good time to nap! It's ok about the computer. Just expensive! And I can't order it until I get my new amazon card in the mail!!
That is a good attitude. Love you.
I'm just remembering that every single person I know is in debt and I'm doing my best to live off very little.
When do u go to G I dr?

Tell daddy I just found an iPhone app exactly like quicken that I can use on my phone for free!! Well it was $1.99 but that's basically free! Also Jason might be able to get me Microsoft office for Mac for free from the studio! That's $100 value!
I'm really excited about the banking thing! It's a checkbook register on my phone!! But it's only going to fuel my addiction!!
I can't believe how great the iPhone is! It does simplify my life!
